By":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krvqOzi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrvqOzi.png&h=002dc61c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n更新左加入更多地標, 遊行路線, 有意見隨時回答, 謝"},{"pid":"c2fca46af38eaea1daec8a23a894380f1da75866","tid":1361642,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0NOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=747a6134\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"0cbc7f7c6ffefa8c212e33ee23cd16fa62b447d7","tid":1361642,"uid":267189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲<br />\n小弟見到好多遍地開花嘅post，好感動<br />\n不同行業嘅巴絲都出嚟發聲<br />\n<br />\n但係因為連登啲post好散同埋facebook接觸到嘅年齡層面相對連登會更加廣<br />\n所以開一個facebook page去整合一啲政府部門同公營機構嘅遍地開花post裡面嘅相<br />\n<br />\n點解淨係整政府部門同公營機構呢？<br />\n因為佢哋發聲嘅震撼力比較大同埋小弟能力有限，未能夠整合晒各行各業嘅post<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲其實只係想post喺連登，而唔想擺喺facebook，歡迎pm我，我會即刻delete返<br />\n<br />\n而如果有喺政府部門或者公營機構工作嘅巴絲想post去facebook，歡迎喺facebook pm呢個page: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivilservantsflowers&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0NOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=90e70855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civilservantsflowers</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"}]}